data.description: Located minutes from downtown Culpeper, this home offers a full unfinished basement with exterior access giving you the potential of future expansion of your living area.  Home offers a large front area as well as a covered front porch. Inside offers nice sized rooms as well as lots of wood flooring.  Grab your agent and see this one today.  Agents, Be sure to review all of the Agent Remarks before showing this home. All showings must have the Buyer's agent present and be scheduled in the MLS.
